graphql.query:
{
    fetchVendors {
        _id
        name
        location
        phoneNumber
        companyName
        email
        address
        city
        pharmacyID
        createdAt
        updatedAt
    }
}

mutation {
    postEmployee(input: {
        firstName: "String",
        lastName: "String",
        dateOfBirth: "String",
        phoneNumber: "String",
        salary: "String",
        email: "String",
        address: "String",
        userID: "String",
    }) {
        _id
        firstName
        lastName
        dateOfBirth
        phoneNumber
        salary
        email
        address
        userID
        error {
            type message
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
    }
}

mutation {
    postVendor(input: {
        name: "String",
        location: "String",
        phoneNumber: "String",
        companyName: "String",
        email: "String",
        address: "String",
        city: "String",
        pharmacyID: "String"
    }) {
        _id
        name
        location
        phoneNumber
        companyName
        email
        address
        city
        pharmacyID
        error {
            type message
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
    }
}

mutation {
    postStore(input: {
        name: "name",
        location: "String",
        manufacturing_date: "String",
        expiry_date: "String",
        quantity: 3,
        pharmacyID: "String",
        isActive: false
        isDisposed: false
    }) {
        _id
        name
        location
        manufacturing_date
        expiry_date
        quantity
        pharmacyID
        isActive
        isDisposed
        error {
            type message
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
    }
}

mutation {
    postItem(input: {
        name: "String",
        scientific_name: "String",
        storage_temperature: "String",
        manufacturer: "String",
        price: 20
        category: "String",
        storeID: "String",
        displayID: "String"
    }) {
        _id
        name
        scientific_name
        storage_temperature
        manufacturer
        price
        category
        storeID
        displayID
        error {
            type message
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
    }
}

mutation {
    removeAllItems {
        _id
        name
        scientific_name
        storage_temperature
        manufacturer
        price
        category
        storeID
        displayID
        createdAt
        updatedAt
    }
}

mutation {
    removeAllVendors {
        _id
        name
        location
        phoneNumber
        companyName
        email
        address
        city
        pharmacyID
        createdAt
        updatedAt
    }
}
